ZH: 我今天买了一张机票去北京。
EN: Today I bought a plane ticket to Beijing.

ZH: 明天你要订机票吗？
EN: Are you booking a plane ticket for tomorrow?

ZH: 我的机票是电子票。
EN: My plane ticket is an e-ticket.

ZH: 我的机票是经济舱。
EN: My plane ticket is for economy class.

ZH: 你可以在网上购买机票。
EN: You can buy plane tickets online.

ZH: 我的机票已经确认了。
EN: My plane ticket has been confirmed.

ZH: 你需要提前预订机票。
EN: You need to book plane tickets in advance.

ZH: 他打算换机票去更早的城市。
EN: He plans to change his plane ticket to an earlier city.

ZH: 这次旅行的机票是谁买的？
EN: Who bought the plane tickets for this trip?

ZH: 我已经买了回程机票。
EN: I have already bought my return plane ticket.

ZH: 请告诉我你的机票信息。
EN: Please tell me your plane ticket information.

ZH: 买机票之前要注意航班时间。
EN: Pay attention to the flight time before buying plane tickets.

ZH: 机票价格会根据需求而变化。
EN: Plane ticket prices will vary based on demand.

ZH: 我还没有确定机票日期。
EN: I haven't finalized the date for my plane ticket yet.

ZH: 机票上有你的姓名和座位号。
EN: Your name and seat number are on the plane ticket.

ZH: 这家航空公司的机票比较便宜。
EN: The plane tickets from this airline are relatively cheap.

ZH: 他的机票是商务舱。
EN: His plane ticket is for business class.

ZH: 请确认你的机票信息是否是正确的。
EN: Please verify that your plane ticket information is correct.

ZH: 机票价格通常在周末更贵。
EN: Plane ticket prices are usually higher on weekends.
